annotationA: Nop2/Sun-like domain containing protein 5 (Nsun5) is predicted to catalyze the m5C-methylation of 28S ribosomal RNA. Nsun5 loss leads to increased lifespan and heat shock resistance; Belongs to the class I-like SAM-binding methyltransferase superfamily. RsmB/NOP family
annotationB: GH27195p; It is involved in the biological process described with: defense response to Gram-negative bacterium; positive regulation of innate immune response
